"Mandatory relates to actions or procedures that people have to do because it is a rule or a law"</span></p><p class="sc-lnPyOc exfzrW pf-39_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-41_">The Oxford Dictionary defines ‘statutory’ and ‘mandatory’ as follows:</span></p><p class="sc-lnPyOc exfzrW pf-42_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-44_">"Statutory - required, permitted, or enacted by statute"
<br><br>
"Mandatory - required by law or mandate; compulsory"</span></p><p class="sc-lnPyOc exfzrW pf-45_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-47_">After reviewing these definitions, we felt that they did not clearly distinguish between "statutory" and "mandatory". Hence, the confusion regarding statutory and mandatory training.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ggpkNl jdwwxc pf-48_ pf-heading-1-h3 _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-50_">What is statutory and mandatory training?</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/whatisthedifferencebetweenstatutoryandmandatorytrainingthemandatorytraininggroupuk1642417021129-1671519057451.jpg?v=1671519098" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/whatisthedifferencebetweenstatutoryandmandatorytrainingthemandatorytraininggroupuk1642417021129-1671519057451.jpg?v=1671519098 1536w" width="5435" height="3623" alt="Mandatory and statutory training courses provider in the UK - Dr Richard Dune - " title="Mandatory and statutory training courses provider in the UK - Dr Richard Dune - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-sLtfs jkHPMQ pf-51_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-lnPyOc exfzrW pf-52_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fThTNe cAYhcc pf-54_">This section will provide more concise definitions of ‘statutory training’ and ‘mandatory training’. We will also give statutory and mandatory training examples, which will help us distinguish between these types.
